cdata.name: DAV
cdata.desc:
DAV is an open source transportation platform. It provides the users with a decentralized marketplace where he can buy or sell transportations services. The DAV protocol links thevehicles, users, and service providersby giving them the tools todiscover, communicate, and transact with each other.

The DAV token is an Ethereum-based (ERC-20) cryptocurrency. It is a utility tokenused to pay for transportation services on the DAV platform.
